com.camerontec.util.collection

Class CollectionUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.collection.CollectionUtils

  • public class CollectionUtils
extends Object
    Utility methods for manipulating Java collections.

    All operations supported by this class are guaranteed not to modify any of their operands, hence the designation as non-destructive.
